 investors institutional investors and overseas asset management companies it manages separate client focused portfolios the firm launches and manages equity fixed income and balanced mutual funds for its clients it also launches and manages hedge funds and etfs for its clients the firm also conducts responsible investing it invests in public equity and fixed income markets across the globe the firm employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with bottomup stock picking approach to create its portfolio it conducts inhouse research to make its inves daiwa asset management co ltd is a privately owned investment manager the firm provides its services to private investors institutional investors and overseas asset management companies it manages separate client focused portfolios the firm launches and manages equity fixed income and balanced mutual funds for its clients it also launches and manages hedge funds and etfs for its clients the firm also conducts responsible investing it invests in public equity and fixed income markets across the globe the firm employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with bottomup stock picking approach to create its portfolio it conducts inhouse research to make its investments the firm was founded on december   and is based in tokyo japan daiwa asset management co ltd operates as a subsidiary of daiwa securities group inc detailed description grantokyo north tower marunouchi chomechiyodakutokyo  japanfounded in  wwwdaiwaamcojp key executives for daiwa asset management co ltd mr nobuyuki iwamoto president age  mr tatsuro inoue principal executive officer of the corporate planning division and director ms seiya miyamoto senior executive managing director mr akihiko kanamura senior executive managing director mr osamu shigeta cpa senior managing director age  compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region  research institute inc asia ace international inc asi